author: Liz S Marin
title: Liz S Marin
text: Paid 28 for unlock was told after 4 days I would need to pay an extra 99 dollars for premium since was not clean imei. Paid 99 more and waited for 7 days, finally received unlock code. Unlocking was very easy once I received the email with unlock code. Just frustrating to wait so many days to receive it.
